      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level for MRL 3.",
      "rationale": "Method of manufactured solutions applied to the incompressible Navier-Stokes solver. Observed order of convergence (1.97) matches theoretical second-order accuracy. Code verification complete at Gradation 2."
